entries.abort: Pilot! Get back here! I will report you to your superior for failing your mission!
entries.arrival_phase_1: Uploading coordinates of Commander Kt'lya's crippled ship now, stand by.
entries.arrival_phase_2: Upload complete, get over there quickly pilot. Dock with him and transfer some spare parts so he can repair his ship.
entries.attack_notify: Tactical Computer: < Incoming fighter vessels. Scans show weapons armed. >
entries.attack_stopped: Tactical Computer: < No more fighter vessels within sensor range. >
entries.complete: Mission complete. Proceed with objectives. Good work, pilot!
entries.failed_destroy: Mission failed! Commander Kt'lya's vessel was destroyed.
entries.panic_1: Pilot! Pay attention! I'm under fire! Get them off my tail!
entries.panic_2: They're on me! Get these bastards off me!
entries.panic_3: I've been hit! Get these vessels off me!
entries.quest_dock_d: Dock with the commanders ship and transfer over some spare parts so he can get his ship running again.
entries.quest_escort_d: Make haste out of the area together with the commander. Make sure that he makes it out safely.
entries.quest_location_d: Although the first attack of the Blacklight pirates were beaten, they are still present in the area and there's bound to be several of them surrounding the place where the SpyNet commander was attacked.
entries.recovery_success: Brother Ezkiel: < Good work, pilot. The commander is now safe. Proceed with further objectives. >
entries.rescue_abandoned: Pilot! Get back here! I will report you to your superior for failing your mission!
entries.rescue_phase_1: Hurry! We have no time to just sit here!
entries.rescue_phase_2: Good, good. Let's get out of here!
entries.split_quest_alert: Brother Ezkiel: < Good work, pilot. We need you to patrol the perimeter for anymore enemy ships. >
entries.taunt_1: We could have just captured you, now we will destroy you!
entries.thanks_1: Whew! Thanks, pilot. It was getting close there for a second!
entries.thanks_2: That was close! Thanks, pilot. I'm glad to be on your team.
entries.thanks_3: It's about time you showed up!
entries.title: Dantooine system: Rescue Commander Kt'lya.
entries.title_d: One of the SpyNet officers have been attacked and disabled. We need you to rescue him before the Blacklight pirates get a shuttle over there to capture him.
